						<summary>

						<p>West wall of the same temple.</p>						

						<p>This inscription in Vaṭṭeḻuttu script of 10th century is a fragment.</p>						

						<p>It appears to record a gift of a <hi rend="italic">nandā</hi> lamp on behalf of a certain Kaṇakkaṅ-kiḻavaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Puruḻamāṇikka-śeṭṭi by the <hi rend="italic">ūrār</hi> who seem to have given 2 <hi rend="italic">mā</hi> of land in this behalf to a certain Piritip-pēraiyaṉ of Ādanūr.</p>						

						</summary>
